OL,5, A council leader and 10 councillors    
OL,6, have quit the Labour Party over Sir    
OL,7, Keir Starmer's decision not to push for
OL,8, a ceasefire in Gaza.                   
OL,10,FBurnley Council leader Afrasiab Anwar, 
OL,11,Fwho had called for the Labour leader to
OL,12,Fresign over the issue, is among those  
OL,13,Fto leave the party.                    
OL,15,FIn a statement, the councillors said   
OL,16,Ftheir memberships were "untenable".    
OL,18,FLabour backs the government's stance of
OL,19,Fcalling for Israel to pause its action 
OL,20,Fagainst Hamas to allow aid into Gaza.  
